{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "methodology": "reverse-dependency-popularity",
  "selection": "Most popular qualifying packages by reverse-dependency count (how many published Elm packages list this package in direct dependencies of their latest elm.json). Pure: direct deps \u2286 {elm/core, elm/json, elm/time, elm/random, elm/bytes, elm/regex, elm/url, elm/parser}. Browser: direct deps \u2286 pure set + {elm/browser, elm/html, elm/svg, elm/virtual-dom, elm/http, elm/file} and \u22651 browser-surface dep. Platform packages (elm/*, elm-explorations/*) excluded as subjects. Failures (kernel/ports/GLSL/mapping/etc.) skipped in popularity order until verified. Expanded beyond the original 200 with host law fixes (Print let-in-record, VirtualDom.Handler adapters, Http named multi-arg fields, NameSub multi-segment expose drop). No pure/browser overlap.",
